> Probably a silly question, but can I reverse the sound channels on my SB
> sound card using software (the driver).
Not trivially afaik. The mmap() interface exposes the true ordering. If you
are in the "one long wire one short wire and wrong side" situation get a 
stereo plug & socket and wire yourself a crossover 
Alan
